---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="KriyagniAI Research Labs">

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>KriyagniAI Research Labs</h1>
    <h2>Where Better Questions Create New Intelligence.</h2>
    <p>
      We blend advanced prompt engineering, structured reasoning, and 
      simulation-driven research to unlock insights hidden beneath the surface. 
      We don’t ask common questions. We ask the questions no one thought to ask.
    </p>

    <div class="buttons">
      <a href="/research" class="btn primary">Explore Our Work</a>
      <a href="/archive" class="btn secondary">Read the Archive</a>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- SUBHEADLINE -->
  <section class="subline">
    <p>
      AI becomes powerful when guided by precision. Our work focuses on building 
      frameworks, prompts, and cognitive architectures that reduce hallucinations 
      and increase truth, clarity, and depth.
    </p>
  </section>


  <!-- MISSION -->
  <section class="mission">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Expand human intelligence by expanding the quality of questions.
      We design prompt systems that think, reason, simulate, and decode 
      reality with higher fidelity. Every breakthrough starts with a question. 
      Our job is to make those questions extraordinary.
    </p>
  </section>


  <!-- WHAT WE DO -->
  <section class="pillars">
    <h2>What We Do</h2>

    <div class="pillar">
      <h3>1. Prompt Engineering Research</h3>
      <p>
        We create high-precision prompt architectures that deliver cleaner logic, 
        transparent reasoning, reduced hallucination, deeper pattern detection, 
        and multi-layer cognition. Prompts aren’t instructions — they are 
        thinking frameworks.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pillar">
      <h3>2. Simulation Intelligence</h3>
      <p>
        Using layered prompt systems, we simulate markets, societies, biotech, 
        psychology, geopolitics, and complex systems. We uncover hidden 
        probabilities, stability patterns, and long-range outcomes with 
        meta-simulation intelligence.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pillar">
      <h3>3. “Questions Never Asked” Archive</h3>
      <p>
        A weekly intelligence drop featuring new questions, cross-domain 
        insights, radical what-ifs, counterfactuals, and deep decoding. 
        This is where original intelligence is born.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
  <section class="philosophy">
    <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
    <p>
      The model matters. But the question matters more.
      Great prompts behave like instruments — calibrated, structured, 
      reasoned, intentional, transparent. We build prompts that expose 
      the invisible: from hidden risks to unseen opportunities, from 
      surface-level facts to structural truths. This is not chatbot prompting. 
      This is research prompting.
    </p>
  </section>


  <!-- SIGNATURE LINES -->
  <section class="quotes">
    <h2>Signature Lines</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>“Better questions. Better intelligence.”</li>
      <li>“Hallucination isn’t a problem. It’s a design flaw.”</li>
      <li>“We engineer cognition, not outputs.”</li>
      <li>“Simulate before you assume.”</li>
      <li>“AI reveals patterns when you ask differently.”</li>
      <li>“The future belongs to the curious.”</li>
      <li>“We turn prompts into precision instruments.”</li>
    </ul>
  </section>


  <!-- FOOTER TAGLINE -->
  <section class="footer-tagline">
    <p>
      KriyagniAI Research Labs — Pushing intelligence forward. 
      One question at a time.
    </p>
  </section>


</Layout>


<style>

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 80px auto 60px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.3em;
  }

  .hero h2 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }

  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #444;
    margin-bottom: 2em;
  }

  .buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 12px 26px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .primary {
    background: black;
    color: white;
  }

  .secondary {
    border: 1px solid #000;
    color: #000;
  }


  /* SUB HEADLINE */
  .subline {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    text-align: center;
    color: #555;
  }


  /* MISSION */
  .mission {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 80px auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mission h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }


  /* PILLARS */
  .pillars {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 80px auto;
  }

  .pillars h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2em;
  }

  .pillar {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .pillar h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }


  /* PHILOSOPHY */
  .philosophy {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 80px auto;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }


  /* SIGNATURE LINES */
  .quotes {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 80px auto;
  }

  .quotes ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quotes li {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }


  /* FOOTER TAGLINE */
  .footer-tagline {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 80px auto 40px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

</style>